1581
01:23:24,333 --> 01:23:27,101
SHAVERS: Ivan Block, you're
under arrest, my friend.

1582
01:23:27,103 --> 01:23:28,335
How's it going, fellas?

1583
01:23:28,337 --> 01:23:29,970
Better than you.

1584
01:23:29,972 --> 01:23:32,706
Money laundering, racketeering,
wire fraud.
(ALL CHUCKLING)

1585
01:23:32,708 --> 01:23:35,242
Look under your feet.
That's American concrete.

1586
01:23:35,244 --> 01:23:37,144
Kiss it, because you'll be
sleeping on it for a long time.

1587
01:23:37,146 --> 01:23:39,046
We'll see.

1588
01:23:39,048 --> 01:23:42,416
That's the great thing about America,
