1589
01:23:42,418 --> 01:23:45,085
Maybe eight months on a
farm, something like that.

1590
01:23:46,421 --> 01:23:47,688
Maybe I'll see
you around, Richie.

1591
01:23:48,490 --> 01:23:49,690
Good luck, sir.

1592
01:23:50,825 --> 01:23:51,925
Get this piece
of shit in the car.

1593
01:23:51,927 --> 01:23:53,293
What about him?

1594
01:23:53,295 --> 01:23:55,062
(CHUCKLING)
Him? He's a cooperator.

1595
01:23:55,064 --> 01:23:56,663
Yeah, don't worry
about him.

1596
01:23:56,665 --> 01:23:58,699
Think about him banging your
girl while you're in jail.

1597
01:23:58,701 --> 01:24:00,134
Now, here's the good part.

1598
01:24:00,136 --> 01:24:02,302
You have the right
to remain silent.

1599
01:24:02,304 --> 01:24:05,439
Anything you say can and will be
used against you in a court of law.

1600
01:24:05,441 --> 01:24:07,574
You have the right
to an attorney.

1601
01:24:07,576 --> 01:24:10,177
If you cannot
afford an attorney,

1602
01:24:10,179 --> 01:24:12,746
